Package business

Class Usecase

java.lang.Object
business.Usecase
All Implemented Interfaces:
Component
public class Usecase extends Object implements Component
Represents a Use Case in a UML diagram. This class implements the Component interface and provides properties such as the name and position of the use case. It also includes methods for displaying the use case and managing its properties and constraints.

The Usecase class is annotated with @JsonIgnoreProperties(ignoreUnknown = true), making it compatible with JSON serialization/deserialization using the Jackson library.
